### Create Order as Admin for Kirkland Megastore
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth-token}}

{
    "status": "CREATED",
    "store": {{store1-id}},
    "items": [
        {"id": "{{lipstick-id}}", "quantity": 25},
        {"id": "{{smartphone-id}}", "quantity": 4}
    ]
}

